  {prompt:"Welche Frage mit Kurzantwort ist komplett richtig?",options:["Is she student? – Yes, she is.","Are they happy? – No, he is not.","Are you tired? – Yes, I are.","Is he here? – Yes, she is."],correct:0,tip:"Pronomen in Frage und Antwort müssen passen (they → they; he → he)",explanation:"✅ <b>Is she a student? – Yes, she is.</b> – Frage-Pronomen (she) = Antwort-Pronomen (she).",d:3}

,
